INSERT INTO `quotes` VALUES (1,'the-only-way-to-do-great','The only way to do great work is to love what you do.','Steve Jobs',2,'2025-11-28 13:26:39','2025-12-10 07:51:21',NULL),(2,'life-is-what-happens-when-youre','Life is what happens when you\'re busy making other plans.','John Lennon',3,'2025-11-28 13:26:39','2025-12-10 07:51:21',NULL),(3,'the-future-belongs-to-those-who','The future belongs to those who believe in the beauty of their dreams.','Eleanor Roosevelt',4,'2025-11-28 13:26:39','2025-12-10 07:51:21',NULL),(4,'it-is-during-our-darkest-moments','It is during our darkest moments that we must focus to see the light.','Aristotle',5,'2025-11-28 13:26:39','2025-12-10 07:51:21',NULL),(5,'be-yourself-everyone-else-is-already','Be yourself; everyone else is already taken.','Oscar Wilde',6,'2025-11-28 13:26:39','2025-12-10 07:51:21',NULL),(6,'the-best-time-to-plant-a','The best time to plant a tree was 20 years ago. The second best time is now.','Chinese Proverb',7,'2025-11-28 13:26:39','2025-12-10 07:51:21',NULL),(7,'man-invented-language-to-satisfy-his','Man invented language to satisfy his deep need to complain.','Lily Tomlin',10,'2025-12-01 06:19:01','2025-12-10 07:51:21',NULL),(8,'i-would-rather-be-a-little','I would rather be a little nobody, then to be an evil somebody.','Abraham Lincoln',10,'2025-12-01 06:19:01','2025-12-10 07:51:21',NULL),(9,'rather-than-waste-time-and-energy','Rather than waste time and energy worrying, use that time and energy to constructively deal with whatever is causing the worry.','Celestine Chua',10,'2025-12-01 06:19:01','2025-12-10 07:51:21',NULL),(10,'life-needs-to-be-more-than','Life needs to be more than just solving problems every day. You need to wake up and be excited about the future.','Elon Musk',10,'2025-12-01 06:19:01','2025-12-10 07:51:22',NULL),(11,'most-of-us-live-our-lives','Most of us live our lives by accident - we live as it happens. Fulfilment comes when we live our lives on purpose.','Simon Sinek',10,'2025-12-01 06:19:01','2025-12-10 07:51:22',NULL),(12,'as-soon-as-you-trust-yourself','As soon as you trust yourself, you will know how to live.','Johann Wolfgang von Goethe',10,'2025-12-01 06:19:01','2025-12-10 07:51:22',NULL),(13,'we-must-learn-to-live-together','We must learn to live together as brothers or perish together as fools.','Martin Luther King, Jr.',10,'2025-12-01 06:19:01','2025-12-10 07:51:22',NULL),(14,'your-hardest-times-often-lead-to','Your hardest times often lead to the greatest moments of your life. Keep going. Tough situations build strong people in the end.','Roy T. Bennett',10,'2025-12-01 06:19:01','2025-12-10 07:51:22',NULL),(15,'originality-is-the-fine-art-of','Originality is the fine art of remembering what you hear but forgetting where you heard it. ','Laurence J. Peter',10,'2025-12-01 06:19:01','2025-12-10 07:51:22',NULL),(16,'dont-hate-the-player-change-the','Don\'t hate the player. Change the game.','Steve Harvey',10,'2025-12-01 06:19:01','2025-12-10 07:51:22',NULL),(17,'i-learned-the-value-of-hard','I learned the value of hard work by working hard. ','Margaret Mead',10,'2025-12-01 06:19:01','2025-12-10 07:51:22',NULL),(18,'progress-is-impossible-without-change-and','Progress is impossible without change, and those who cannot change their minds cannot change anything.','George Bernard Shaw',10,'2025-12-01 06:19:01','2025-12-10 07:51:22',NULL),(19,'new-opinions-are-always-suspected-and','New opinions are always suspected, and usually opposed, without any other reason but because they are not common.','John Locke',10,'2025-12-01 06:19:01','2025-12-10 07:51:22',NULL),(20,'what-have-you-done-today-to','What have you done today to make someone else happy?','Deepam Chaterjee',10,'2025-12-01 06:19:01','2025-12-10 07:51:22',NULL),(21,'if-you-believe-you-can-you','If you believe you can, you can. If you believe you can\'t, then, well you can\'t.','Celestine Chua',10,'2025-12-01 06:19:01','2025-12-10 07:51:22',NULL),(22,'great-deeds-are-usually-wrought-at','Great deeds are usually wrought at great risks.','Herodotus',10,'2025-12-01 06:19:01','2025-12-10 07:51:22',NULL),(23,'nature-loves-to-hide','Nature loves to hide.','Heraclitus',10,'2025-12-01 06:19:01','2025-12-10 07:51:22',NULL),(24,'when-we-allow-negative-messages-to','When we allow negative messages to fester in our head, they take on a life of their own.','Lolly Daskal',10,'2025-12-01 06:19:01','2025-12-10 07:51:22',NULL),(25,'no-need-to-hurry-no-need','No need to hurry. No need to sparkle. No need to be anybody but oneself.','Virginia Woolf',10,'2025-12-01 06:19:01','2025-12-10 07:51:22',NULL),(26,'growing-up-is-losing-some-illusions','Growing up is losing some illusions, in order to acquire others.','Virginia Woolf',10,'2025-12-01 06:19:01','2025-12-10 07:51:22',NULL),(27,'the-secret-of-happiness-is-not','The secret of happiness is not in doing what you like but in liking what you have to do.','Sathya Sai Baba',10,'2025-12-01 06:19:01','2025-12-10 07:51:22',NULL),(28,'were-responsible-for-everything-that-happens','We\'re responsible for everything that happens to us.','Yanni',10,'2025-12-01 06:19:01','2025-12-10 07:51:22',NULL),(29,'happiness-is-the-meaning-and-the','Happiness is the meaning and the purpose of life, the whole aim and end of human existence.','Aristotle',10,'2025-12-01 06:19:01','2025-12-10 07:51:22',NULL),(30,'its-wise-to-tell-the-truth','It\'s wise to tell the truth. It\'s even wiser to tell it kindly.','Maxime Lagace',10,'2025-12-01 06:19:01','2025-12-10 07:51:22',NULL),(31,'you-can-calculate-the-worth-of','You can calculate the worth of a man by the number of his enemies.','Gustave Flaubert',10,'2025-12-01 06:19:01','2025-12-10 07:51:22',NULL),(32,'there-are-only-encounters-in-history','There are only encounters in history. There are no accidents.','Pablo Picasso',10,'2025-12-01 06:19:01','2025-12-10 07:51:22',NULL),(33,'every-one-of-us-is-the','Every one of us is the sum total of his own thoughts.','Earl Nightingale',10,'2025-12-01 06:19:01','2025-12-10 07:51:22',NULL),(34,'the-only-thing-new-in-the','The only thing new in the world is the history you do not know.','Harry S. Truman',10,'2025-12-01 06:19:01','2025-12-10 07:51:22',NULL),(35,'the-only-problem-we-really-have','The only problem we really have is we think we\'re not supposed to have problems! Problems call us to higher level- - face & solve them now!','Tony Robbins',10,'2025-12-01 06:19:01','2025-12-10 07:51:22',NULL),(36,'be-yourself-everyone-else-is-already-2','Be yourself; everyone else is already taken ','Oscar Wilde',10,'2025-12-01 06:19:01','2025-12-10 07:51:22',NULL),(37,'everything-youve-ever-wanted-is-on','Everything you\'ve ever wanted is on the other side of fear.','Brian Tracy',10,'2025-12-01 06:19:01','2025-12-10 07:51:22',NULL),(38,'always-show-more-kindness-than-seems','Always show more kindness than seems necessary because the person receiving it needs it more than you will ever know.','Colin Powell',10,'2025-12-01 06:19:01','2025-12-10 07:51:22',NULL),(39,'i-alone-cannot-change-the-world','I alone cannot change the world, but I can cast a stone across the waters to create many ripples.','Mother Teresa',10,'2025-12-01 06:19:01','2025-12-10 07:51:22',NULL),(40,'the-reward-of-suffering-is-experience','The reward of suffering is experience.','Harry S. Truman',10,'2025-12-01 06:19:01','2025-12-10 07:51:22',NULL),(41,'wit-is-educated-insolence','Wit is educated insolence.','Aristotle',10,'2025-12-01 06:19:01','2025-12-10 07:51:22',NULL),(42,'your-spirit-is-the-true-shield','Your spirit is the true shield.','Morihei Ueshiba',10,'2025-12-01 06:19:01','2025-12-10 07:51:22',NULL),(43,'dont-cry-because-its-over-smile','Don\'t cry because it\'s over. Smile because it happened.','Dr. Seuss',10,'2025-12-01 06:19:01','2025-12-10 07:51:22',NULL),(44,'keep-away-from-people-who-try','Keep away from people who try to belittle your ambitions.','Mark Twain',10,'2025-12-01 06:19:01','2025-12-10 07:51:22',NULL),(45,'fear-is-a-natural-reaction-to','Fear is a natural reaction to moving closer to the truth.','Pema Chodron',10,'2025-12-01 06:19:01','2025-12-10 07:51:22',NULL),(46,'even-if-you-stumble-and-fall','Even if you stumble and fall down, it doesn\'t mean you\'ve chosen the wrong path.','Zen Proverb',10,'2025-12-01 06:19:01','2025-12-10 07:51:22',NULL),(47,'do-what-is-right-not-what','Do what is right, not what is easy, nor what is popular.','Roy T. Bennett',10,'2025-12-01 06:19:01','2025-12-10 07:51:22',NULL),(48,'conflict-cannot-survive-without-your-participation','Conflict cannot survive without your participation. ','Wayne Dyer',10,'2025-12-01 06:19:01','2025-12-10 07:51:22',NULL),(49,'the-path-is-difficult-to-ensure','The path is difficult to ensure worthiness. The lazy look elsewhere, The persevering find riches.','Ming-Dao Deng',10,'2025-12-01 06:19:01','2025-12-10 07:51:22',NULL),(50,'some-men-see-things-as-they','Some men see things as they are and ask why. Others dream things that never were and ask why not.','George Bernard Shaw',10,'2025-12-01 06:19:01','2025-12-10 07:51:22',NULL),(51,'leaders-spend-5-of-their-time','Leaders spend 5% of their time on the problem & 95% of their time on the solution. Get over it & crush it!','Tony Robbins',10,'2025-12-01 06:19:01','2025-12-10 07:51:22',NULL),(52,'today-i-begin-a-new-life','Today I begin a new life. I will greet this day with love in my heart.','Og Mandino',10,'2025-12-01 06:19:01','2025-12-10 07:51:22',NULL),(53,'the-most-effective-way-to-do','The most effective way to do it, is to do it.','Amelia Earhart',10,'2025-12-01 06:19:01','2025-12-10 07:51:22',NULL),(54,'in-the-middle-of-chaos-lies','In the middle of chaos lies opportunity.  ','Bruce Lee',10,'2025-12-01 06:19:01','2025-12-10 07:51:22',NULL),(55,'the-key-to-success-is-action','The key to success is action.','Brian Tracy',10,'2025-12-01 06:19:01','2025-12-10 07:51:22',NULL),(56,'success-is-not-what-you-do','Success is not what you do when you are on top.  Success is how high you bounce when you hit the bottom.','Sonia Ricotti',10,'2025-12-01 06:19:01','2025-12-10 07:51:22',NULL),(57,'the-only-place-where-success-comes','The only place where success comes before work is in the dictionary.','Vidal Sassoon',7,'2025-12-01 06:19:53','2025-12-10 07:51:22',NULL),(58,'stop-acting-so-small-you-are','Stop acting so small. You are the universe in ecstatic motion.','Rumi',7,'2025-12-01 06:19:53','2025-12-10 07:51:22',NULL),(59,'know-your-gifts-and-share-them','Know your gifts and share them.','Les Brown',7,'2025-12-01 06:19:53','2025-12-10 07:51:22',NULL),(60,'a-mans-worth-is-no-greater','A man\'s worth is no greater than his ambitions.','Marcus Aurelius',7,'2025-12-01 06:19:53','2025-12-10 07:51:22',NULL),(61,'the-most-virtuous-are-those-who','The most virtuous are those who content themselves with being virtuous without seeking to appear so.','Plato',7,'2025-12-01 06:19:53','2025-12-10 07:51:22',NULL),(62,'nothing-can-survive-without-food-everything','Nothing can survive without food. Everything we consume acts either to heal us or to poison us.','Thich Nhat Hanh',7,'2025-12-01 06:19:53','2025-12-10 07:51:22',NULL),(63,'great-thoughts-speak-only-to-the','Great thoughts speak only to the thoughtful mind, but great actions speak to all mankind.','Theodore Roosevelt',7,'2025-12-01 06:19:53','2025-12-10 07:51:22',NULL),(64,'truth-is-like-most-opinions-best','Truth is like most opinions - best unexpressed.','Kenneth Branagh',7,'2025-12-01 06:19:53','2025-12-10 07:51:22',NULL),(65,'the-least-deviation-from-truth-will','The least deviation from truth will be multiplied later.','Aristotle',7,'2025-12-01 06:19:53','2025-12-10 07:51:22',NULL),(66,'its-always-to-soon-to-quit','It\'s always to soon to quit!','Norman Vincent Peale',7,'2025-12-01 06:19:53','2025-12-10 07:51:22',NULL),(67,'no-one-can-hurt-you-without','No one can hurt you without your consent.','Eleanor Roosevelt',7,'2025-12-01 06:19:53','2025-12-10 07:51:22',NULL),(68,'remember-that-the-best-relationship-is','Remember that the best relationship is one in which your love for each other exceeds your need for each other.','Dalai Lama',7,'2025-12-01 06:19:53','2025-12-10 07:51:22',NULL),(69,'the-world-makes-way-for-the','The world makes way for the man who knows where he is going.','Ralph Waldo Emerson',7,'2025-12-01 06:19:53','2025-12-10 07:51:22',NULL),(70,'youre-on-earth-theres-no-cure','You\'re on earth. There\'s no cure for that.','Samuel Beckett',7,'2025-12-01 06:19:53','2025-12-10 07:51:22',NULL),(71,'dont-cry-because-its-over-smile-2','Don\'t cry because it\'s over. Smile because it happened.','Dr. Seuss',7,'2025-12-01 06:19:53','2025-12-10 07:51:22',NULL),(72,'you-get-paid-in-direct-proportion','You get paid in direct proportion to the difficulty of problems you solve.','Elon Musk',7,'2025-12-01 06:19:53','2025-12-10 07:51:22',NULL),(73,'it-is-easy-to-love-your','It is easy to love your friend, but sometimes the hardest lesson to learn is to love your enemy.','Sun Tzu',7,'2025-12-01 06:19:53','2025-12-10 07:51:22',NULL),(74,'you-are-the-average-of-the','You are the average of the five people you spend the most time with.','Jim Rohn',7,'2025-12-01 06:19:53','2025-12-10 07:51:22',NULL),(75,'honor-is-the-foundation-of-courage','Honor is the foundation of courage.','Amelia Earhart',7,'2025-12-01 06:19:53','2025-12-10 07:51:22',NULL),(76,'darkness-cannot-drive-out-darkness-only','Darkness cannot drive out darkness; only light can do that. Hate cannot drive out hate; only love can do that.','Martin Luther King, Jr.',7,'2025-12-01 06:19:53','2025-12-10 07:51:22',NULL),(77,'if-you-let-your-head-get','If you let your head get too big, it\'ll break your neck.','Elvis Presley',7,'2025-12-01 06:19:53','2025-12-10 07:51:22',NULL),(78,'try-all-things-hold-fast-that','Try all things, hold fast that which is good.','John Locke',7,'2025-12-01 06:19:53','2025-12-10 07:51:22',NULL),(79,'be-grateful-for-what-you-have','Be grateful for what you have now, and nothing should be taken for granted.','Roy T. Bennett',7,'2025-12-01 06:19:53','2025-12-10 07:51:22',NULL),(80,'always-forgive-your-enemies-nothing-annoys','Always forgive your enemies - nothing annoys them so much. ','Oscar Wilde',7,'2025-12-01 06:19:53','2025-12-10 07:51:22',NULL),(81,'as-you-grow-older-you-will','As you grow older you will discover that you have two hands. One for helping yourself, the other for helping others.','Audrey Hepburn',7,'2025-12-01 06:19:53','2025-12-10 07:51:22',NULL),(82,'every-experience-is-a-lesson-every','Every experience is a lesson. Every loss is a gain.','Sathya Sai Baba',7,'2025-12-01 06:19:53','2025-12-10 07:51:22',NULL),(83,'you-become-a-worrier-by-practicing','You become a worrier by practicing worry. You become free of worry by practicing the opposite.','Norman Vincent Peale',7,'2025-12-01 06:19:53','2025-12-10 07:51:22',NULL),(84,'things-turn-out-best-for-the','Things turn out best for the people who make the best of the way things turn out.','John Wooden',7,'2025-12-01 06:19:53','2025-12-10 07:51:22',NULL),(85,'every-man-desires-to-live-long','Every man desires to live long, but no man wishes to be old.','Jonathan Swift',7,'2025-12-01 06:19:53','2025-12-10 07:51:22',NULL),(86,'do-the-difficult-things-while-they','Do the difficult things while they are easy and do the great things while they are small.','Lao Tzu',7,'2025-12-01 06:19:53','2025-12-10 07:51:22',NULL),(87,'theres-no-next-time-its-now','There\'s no next time. It\'s now or never.','Celestine Chua',7,'2025-12-01 06:19:53','2025-12-10 07:51:22',NULL),(88,'to-injure-an-opponent-is-to','To injure an opponent is to injure yourself. To control aggression without inflicting injury is the Art of Peace.','Morihei Ueshiba',7,'2025-12-01 06:19:53','2025-12-10 07:51:22',NULL),(89,'youre-braver-than-you-believe-and','You\'re braver than you believe, and stronger than you seem, and smarter than you think.','A.A. Milne',7,'2025-12-01 06:19:53','2025-12-10 07:51:22',NULL),(90,'be-not-afraid-of-growing-slowly','Be not afraid of growing slowly, be afraid only of standing still. ','Chinese Proverb',7,'2025-12-01 06:19:53','2025-12-10 07:51:22',NULL),(91,'rich-people-have-small-tvs-and','Rich people have small TVs and big libraries, and poor people have small libraries and big TVs.','Zig Ziglar',7,'2025-12-01 06:19:53','2025-12-10 07:51:22',NULL),(92,'all-religions-arts-and-sciences-are','All religions, arts and sciences are branches of the same tree. ','Albert Einstein',7,'2025-12-01 06:19:53','2025-12-10 07:51:22',NULL),(93,'wise-men-speak-because-they-have','Wise men speak because they have something to say; Fools because they have to say something.','Plato',7,'2025-12-01 06:19:53','2025-12-10 07:51:22',NULL),(94,'your-happiness-is-what-truly-matters','Your happiness is what truly matters most. Do what you have to do in order to be happy.','Brian Tracy',7,'2025-12-01 06:19:53','2025-12-10 07:51:22',NULL),(95,'the-energy-of-the-mind-is','The energy of the mind is the essence of life.','Aristotle',7,'2025-12-01 06:19:53','2025-12-10 07:51:22',NULL),(96,'make-your-mind-your-own-business','Make your mind your own business.','Jack Butcher',7,'2025-12-01 06:19:53','2025-12-10 07:51:22',NULL),(97,'we-ourselves-feel-that-what-we','We ourselves feel that what we are doing is just a drop in the ocean. But the ocean would be less because of that missing drop.','Mother Teresa',7,'2025-12-01 06:19:53','2025-12-10 07:51:22',NULL),(98,'time-you-enjoy-wasting-was-not','Time you enjoy wasting, was not wasted.','John Lennon',7,'2025-12-01 06:19:53','2025-12-10 07:51:22',NULL),(99,'people-seldom-do-what-they-believe','People seldom do what they believe in. They do what is convenient, then repent.','Bob Dylan',7,'2025-12-01 06:19:53','2025-12-10 07:51:22',NULL),(100,'in-life-you-need-either-inspiration','In life you need either inspiration or desperation.','Tony Robbins',7,'2025-12-01 06:19:53','2025-12-10 07:51:22',NULL),(101,'never-be-afraid-to-raise-your','Never be afraid