INSERT INTO `quotes` VALUES (5672,'there-is-no-value-in-anything-3','There is no value in anything until it is finished. ','Genghis Khan',65,'2025-12-01 07:59:05','2025-12-10 07:52:38',NULL),(5673,'coming-together-is-a-beginning-staying-2','Coming together is a beginning, staying together is progress, and working together is success. ','Henry Ford',65,'2025-12-01 07:59:05','2025-12-10 07:51:43',NULL),(5674,'one-of-the-first-signs-of-2','One of the first signs of the beginning of understanding is the wish to die. ','Franz Kafka',65,'2025-12-01 07:59:05','2025-12-10 07:51:43',NULL),(5675,'someone-who-points-out-your-flaws-4','Someone who points out your flaws to you is not necessarily your enemy. Someone who speaks of your virtues is not necessarily your friend.','Zen Proverb',65,'2025-12-01 07:59:05','2025-12-10 07:52:38',NULL),(5676,'doubt-is-an-uncomfortable-condition-but-2','Doubt is an uncomfortable condition, but certainty is a ridiculous one.','Voltaire',65,'2025-12-01 07:59:05','2025-12-10 07:51:43',NULL),(5677,'among-the-things-you-can-give-3','Among the things you can give and still keep are your word, a smile, and a grateful heart.','Zig Ziglar',65,'2025-12-01 07:59:05','2025-12-10 07:52:38',NULL),(5678,'whenever-you-do-a-thing-act-3','Whenever you do a thing, act as if all the world were watching.','Thomas Jefferson',65,'2025-12-01 07:59:05','2025-12-10 07:52:38',NULL),(5679,'difficult-and-meaningful-will-always-bring-4','Difficult and meaningful will always bring more satisfaction than easy and meaningless.','Maxime Lagace',65,'2025-12-01 07:59:05','2025-12-10 07:52:38',NULL),(5680,'some-people-feel-the-rain-others-4','Some people feel the rain. Others just get wet. ','Bob Dylan',65,'2025-12-01 07:59:05','2025-12-10 07:52:38',NULL),(5681,'when-you-love-someone-you-love-3','When you love someone, you love the person as they are, and not as you\'d like them to be.','Leo Tolstoy',65,'2025-12-01 07:59:05','2025-12-10 07:52:38',NULL),(5682,'anger-begins-with-folly-and-ends-2','Anger begins with folly, and ends with repentance. ','Beverly Sills',65,'2025-12-01 07:59:05','2025-12-10 07:51:43',NULL),(5683,'everything-you-look-at-can-become-3','Everything you look at can become a fairy tale and you can get a story from everything you touch.','Hans Christian Andersen',65,'2025-12-01 07:59:05','2025-12-10 07:52:38',NULL),(5684,'you-must-conceive-it-in-your-3','You must conceive it in your heart and mind before you can receive it. If you believe then all things are possible.','Norman Vincent Peale',65,'2025-12-01 07:59:05','2025-12-10 07:52:38',NULL),(5685,'everything-has-its-beauty-but-not-4','Everything has its beauty, but not everyone sees it. ','Confucius',65,'2025-12-01 07:59:05','2025-12-10 07:52:38',NULL),(5686,'every-night-before-going-to-sleep-4','Every night before going to sleep, we must ask ourselves: what weakness did I overcome today? What virtue did I acquire?','Seneca',65,'2025-12-01 07:59:05','2025-12-10 07:52:38',NULL),(5687,'to-understand-the-heart-and-mind-4','To understand the heart and mind of a person, look not at what he has already achieved, but at what he aspires to.','Kahlil Gibran',65,'2025-12-01 07:59:05','2025-12-10 07:52:38',NULL),(5688,'your-chances-of-success-in-any-2','Your chances of success in any undertaking can always be measured by your belief in yourself.','Robert Collier',65,'2025-12-01 07:59:05','2025-12-10 07:51:43',NULL),(5689,'the-only-problem-we-really-have-3','The only problem we really have is we think we\'re not supposed to have problems! Problems call us to higher level- - face & solve them now!','Tony Robbins',65,'2025-12-01 07:59:05','2025-12-10 07:52:38',NULL),(5690,'the-most-difficult-thing-is-the-3','The most difficult thing is the decision to act, the rest is merely tenacity. The fears are paper tigers.','Amelia Earhart',65,'2025-12-01 07:59:05','2025-12-10 07:52:38',NULL),(5691,'teamwork-the-fuel-that-allows-common','TEAMWORK: the fuel that allows common people attain uncommon results.','Andrew Carnegie',65,'2025-12-01 07:59:05','2025-12-10 07:51:43',NULL),(5692,'i-try-more-and-more-to-5','I try more and more to be myself, caring relatively little whether people approve or disapprove.','Vincent van Gogh',65,'2025-12-01 07:59:05','2025-12-10 07:52:38',NULL),(5693,'success-is-good-at-any-age','Success is good at any age, but the sooner you find it, the longer you will enjoy it.','Napoleon Hill',65,'2025-12-01 07:59:05','2025-12-10 07:51:43',NULL),(5694,'what-we-call-the-beginning-is','What we call the beginning is often the end. And to make an end is to make a beginning. The end is where we start from.','T.S. Eliot',65,'2025-12-01 07:59:05','2025-12-10 07:51:43',NULL),(5695,'it-is-better-to-fail-in-5','It is better to fail in originality than to succeed in imitation.','Herman Melville',65,'2025-12-01 07:59:05','2025-12-10 07:52:38',NULL),(5696,'every-moment-you-get-is-a-2','Every moment you get is a gift. Spend it on things that matter. Don\'t spend it by dwelling on unhappy things.','Celestine Chua',65,'2025-12-01 07:59:05','2025-12-10 07:51:43',NULL),(5697,'surround-yourself-with-only-people-who','Surround yourself with only people who are going to lift you higher. ','Oprah Winfrey',65,'2025-12-01 07:59:05','2025-12-10 07:51:43',NULL),(5698,'it-is-never-too-late-to-2','It is never too late to be what you might have been.','George Eliot',65,'2025-12-01 07:59:05','2025-12-10 07:51:43',NULL),(5699,'one-small-positive-thought-can-change-3','One small positive thought can change your whole day.','Zig Ziglar',65,'2025-12-01 07:59:05','2025-12-10 07:52:38',NULL),(5700,'when-you-are-totally-at-peace-2','When you are totally at peace with yourself, nothing can shake you.','Deepam Chaterjee',65,'2025-12-01 07:59:05','2025-12-10 07:51:44',NULL),(5701,'the-wise-warrior-avoids-the-battle-4','The wise warrior avoids the battle.','Sun Tzu',65,'2025-12-01 07:59:05','2025-12-10 07:52:38',NULL),(5702,'learn-to-value-yourself-which-means-3','Learn to 