e you are planted!','Mary Engelbreit',9,'2025-12-01 07:59:57','2025-12-10 07:52:38',NULL),(5724,'dont-look-back-youre-not-going-3','Don\'t look back - you\'re not going that way.','Mary Engelbreit',9,'2025-12-01 07:59:57','2025-12-10 07:52:38',NULL),(5725,'we-ourselves-feel-that-what-we-3','We ourselves feel that what we are doing is just a drop in the ocean. But the ocean would be less because of that missing drop.','Mother Teresa',9,'2025-12-01 07:59:57','2025-12-10 07:52:38',NULL),(5726,'formal-education-will-make-you-a-3','Formal education will make you a living, self-education will make you a fortune.','Jim Rohn',9,'2025-12-01 07:59:57','2025-12-10 07:52:38',NULL),(5727,'a-man-is-not-called-wise-2','A man is not called wise because he talks and talks again; but if he is peaceful, loving and fearless then he is in truth called wise. ','Buddha',9,'2025-12-01 07:59:57','2025-12-10 07:51:44',NULL),(5728,'time-and-health-are-two-precious','Time and health are two precious assets that we don\'t recognize and appreciate until they have been depleted. ','Denis Waitley',9,'2025-12-01 07:59:57','2025-12-10 07:51:44',NULL),(5729,'change-the-changeable-accept-the-unchangeable-2','Change the changeable, accept the unchangeable, and remove yourself from the unacceptable. ','Denis Waitley',9,'2025-12-01 07:59:57','2025-12-10 07:51:44',NULL),(5730,'thinking-will-not-overcome-fear-but-2','Thinking will not overcome fear but action will. ','W. Clement Stone',9,'2025-12-01 07:59:57','2025-12-10 07:51:44',NULL),(5731,'peace-of-mind-is-that-mental-3','Peace of mind is that mental condition in which you have accepted the worst.','Lin Yutang',9,'2025-12-01 07:59:57','2025-12-10 07:52:38',NULL),(5732,'whenever-you-find-yourself-on-the-2','Whenever you find yourself on the side of the majority, it is time to reform.','Mark Twain',9,'2025-12-01 07:59:57','2025-12-10 07:51:44',NULL),(5733,'dont-let-the-noise-of-others-6','Don\'t let the noise of others\' opinions drown out your own inner voice.','Steve Jobs',9,'2025-12-01 07:59:57','2025-12-10 07:52:38',NULL),(5734,'quality-is-not-an-act-it-4','Quality is not an act, it is a habit.','Aristotle',9,'2025-12-01 07:59:57','2025-12-10 07:52:38',NULL),(5735,'develop-success-from-failures-discouragement-and-4','Develop success from failures. Discouragement and failure are two of the surest stepping stones to success.','Dale Carnegie',9,'2025-12-01 07:59:57','2025-12-10 07:52:38',NULL),(5736,'attitude-not-aptitude-determines-altitude-4','Attitude, not aptitude, determines altitude.  ','Zig Ziglar',9,'2025-12-01 07:59:57','2025-12-10 07:52:38',NULL),(5737,'we-have-a-duty-to-maintain-6','We have a duty to maintain the light of consciousness to make sure it continues into the future.','Elon Musk',9,'2025-12-01 07:59:57','2025-12-10 07:52:38',NULL),(5738,'welcome-every-morning-with-a-smile-3','Welcome every morning with a smile. Look on the new day as another gift from your Creator, another golden opportunity.','Og Mandino',9,'2025-12-01 07:59:57','2025-12-10 07:52:38',NULL),(5739,'to-forget-the-whole-world-is-2','To forget the whole world is easy; to make the whole world forget you is hard.','Zhuangzi',9,'2025-12-01 07:59:57','2025-12-10 07:51:44',NULL),(5740,'the-present-moment-dies-every-moment-2','The present moment dies every moment to become the past , is reborn every moment into the future. All experience is now. Now never ends.','Deepak Chopra',9,'2025-12-01 07:59:57','2025-12-10 07:51:44',NULL),(5741,'there-is-no-value-in-anything-4','There is no value in anything until it is finished. ','Genghis Khan',9,'2025-12-01 07:59:57','2025-12-10 07:52:38',NULL),(5742,'every-limit-is-a-beginning-as-2','Every limit is a beginning as well as an ending.','George Eliot',9,'2025-12-01 07:59:57','2025-12-10 07:51:44',NULL),(5743,'change-yourself-you-are-in-control','Change yourself - you are in control.','Mahatma Gandhi',9,'2025-12-01 07:59:57','2025-12-10 07:51:44',NULL),(5744,'when-you-are-talented-you-do-2','When